trans-unit.source: Indicates that there was an error downloading either the [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] manifests or the deployment's files to the client computer.
trans-unit.target: Indikerer at det oppstod en feil under nedlasting av enten den [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] programmanifest eller den distribusjonen filer til klientdatamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: A DeploymentDownloadException can indicate that a number of problems occurred when the user tried to download a [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] application update: - The client's computer's network connection is down.
trans-unit.target: En DeploymentDownloadException kan tyde på at en rekke problemer oppstod under brukeren prøvde å laste ned en [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] appoppdateringen:-klientens datamaskinens nettverksforbindelse er nede.

trans-unit.source: - The Web server, FTP server, or file share hosting the update is unavailable.
trans-unit.target: -Nettserveren FTP-server eller filressurs vert oppdateringen er utilgjengelig.

trans-unit.source: - One or more of the files in the [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] deployment was not found.
trans-unit.target: -En eller flere av filene i den [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] distribusjon ble ikke funnet.

trans-unit.source: To obtain detailed error information about an exception, consult the [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] error log.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha detaljert informasjon om feilen om et unntak, kan du se den [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] feilloggen.
Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [feilsøking ClickOnce distribusjoner](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
